 current simulations do not sufficiently reproduce\ndiverse merger histories and their effects on satellite populations. Explaining\nthe emergence of this relation is therefore essential for obtaining a complete\nunderstanding of galaxy formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 17:59:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 18:04:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
