 $\\simeq\n10^{11}$~GeV ($10^{10}$~GeV) if the magnetic energy density is large (and the\nVHE component is correspondingly weak). These high energies are possible by\ndecoupling the production regions of UHECR and gamma-rays in our multizone\nmodel. Finally, we find basic consistency with the energy budget needed to\naccommodate the UHECR origin from ll-GRBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 18:03:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 13:15:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Mar 2022 14:14:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
