gand chemistry and surface heterogeneity\nin determining paths to favorable doping in quantum dots, an observation that\nwill be general to other III-V and II-VI quantum dot systems generally\nsynthesized with carboxylate ligands.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jul 2021 22:17:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-13"}
